## User Review Required

> [!NOTE]
> I have chosen SQLite for the database because it's portable and requires zero setup on your end. If you prefer MongoDB, PostgreSQL, or another database, please let me know!

## Verification Plan
### Manual Verification
- Start the backend on port 5000.
- Start the frontend.
- Attempt to sign up a new user via the UI.
- Verify the user is inserted into the `users` table.
- Attempt to log in with the new credentials.
- Verify a JWT is returned and the user is redirected to the dashboard.
